{"tid":1718980,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"好重要 有個問題要改","createTime":"2019-11-14T03:38:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-14T11:06:37.000Z","uid":161090,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"17d27e131d263d050e3c6dca142e87f04e815855","tid":1718980,"uid":161090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:38:10.000Z","msg":"你地覺唔覺日日都發生緊啲好離譜既事<br />\n所以焦點係咁轉黎轉去<br />\n<br />\n但係有啲野其實未解決  我覺得唔可以全部人一齊轉移視線<br />\n<br />\n要有一部分人 針對前一件事 <br />\n<br />\n例如：有狗亂射 （佢地啲仔女都未還） 但全部人轉晒視線落中大  <br />\n<br />\n我唔係話新既事唔洗理  但有啲舊既要處理左先 <br />\n<br />\n如果唔係啲狗就唔會驚  因為香港人太善忘"},{"pid":"b96ffd1de7f9c4f23ec9db1788660c23aadf8233","tid":1718980,"uid":161090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:39:56.000Z","msg":"我明白好多新問題出現<br />\n<br />\n但舊既次次都係處理一半 <br />\n好快啲人就唔記得 <br />\n咁樣會冇阻嚇作用"},{"pid":"da7cd9684599375bef1dc74bb8f7ed380cf6395a","tid":1718980,"uid":161090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T03:47:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e704327fd10d861f0badd653651b179d2754b479","tid":1718980,"uid":161090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T04:05:47.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1bcb0e752959f406aeb7cf1047fc1005e92bf948","tid":1718980,"uid":161090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:33:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8a5b79f6efd8d4cc7ffa157d79e9dca9087c47fe","tid":1718980,"uid":323962,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T05:37:33.000Z","msg":"同埋我想講<br />\n2014年輸就係輸無bewater<br />\n無比大眾休息過正常生活嘅機會<br />\n而家大學一役之後<br />\n又佔領大學又長期堵路<br />\n警察刻意唔執法<br />\n唔係就係2014翻版咩？"},{"pid":"5c5c007340a8e53d5b5b77c0b39ecb38669ff980","tid":1718980,"uid":161090,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T11:06:37.000Z","msg":"Push"}]}